data.name: Dragonmaid Hospitality
data.desc: Special Summon 1 "Dragonmaid" monster from your hand or GY in Defense Position, then, you can send 1 "Dragonmaid" monster with the same Attribute, but a different Level, from your Deck to the GY. You can only activate 1 "Dragonmaid Hospitality" per turn.
